    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334760/extras/7b35d0f9926e0266e91668e3afbf8d56.poster.avif?t=1771500192\" width=612 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334760/extras/7b35d0f9926e0266e91668e3afbf8d56.webm?t=1771500192\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334760/extras/7b35d0f9926e0266e91668e3afbf8d56.mp4?t=1771500192\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>真实物理反馈</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >前沿物理引擎带来智能动态物理和真实连锁反应，还有精准操控手感加持。借助墙壁反弹的冲击力，将敌人撞下深渊，感受动量传递的暴力美学。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334760/extras/1cfa09f7bcf61a983882723eea5a1c2e.poster.avif?t=1771500192\" width=612 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334760/extras/1cfa09f7bcf61a983882723eea5a1c2e.webm?t=1771500192\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334760/extras/1cfa09f7bcf61a983882723eea5a1c2e.mp4?t=1771500192\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>不可思议的英雄组合</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >命运让八竿子打不着的两人结伴而行，攀登《Awaysis》漂浮的山脉。探索玄秘神庙的失落秘宝，挑战暗影黑魔王，恢复世界的平衡。而这场狂野冒险的第一步……得先想办法说动那只赖在温泉里不出来的青蛙！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334760/extras/742b940111c4b5719e19d8e40bbbd413.poster.avif?t=1771500192\" width=612 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334760/extras/742b940111c4b5719e19d8e40bbbd413.webm?t=1771500192\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334760/extras/742b940111c4b5719e19d8e40bbbd413.mp4?t=1771500192\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>魔幻乱世</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索古老魔法与现代纷争并存的迷人世界。《Awaysis》的动态难度系统将不断考验你的战斗实力，一路击败敌人（甚至盟友）方可获得魔法神器。唯有最无畏之人，才能夺得至宝！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334760/extras/1cfa09f7bcf61a983882723eea5a1c2e.poster.avif?t=1771500192\" width=612 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334760/extras/1cfa09f7bcf61a983882723eea5a1c2e.webm?t=1771500192\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334760/extras/1cfa09f7bcf61a983882723eea5a1c2e.mp4?t=1771500192\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>独领风骚的原声带</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >传奇音乐大师田中宏和（代表作《银河战士》《地球冒险》《任天堂明星大乱斗X》）亲自操刀，劲爆节奏嗨翻全场。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334760/extras/5b3b27aa6df00c3db37664945f5631ec.poster.avif?t=1771500192\" width=612 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334760/extras/5b3b27aa6df00c3db37664945f5631ec.webm?t=1771500192\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334760/extras/5b3b27aa6df00c3db37664945f5631ec.mp4?t=1771500192\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
